criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 60 years

          -  Sign free and informed consent;

          -  Demonstrate interest, conditions and availability to participate in all procedures
             included in the study protocol;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Refusal to participate;

          -  Patients who have not undergone cognitive testing;

          -  Physical amputation;

          -  Patients undergoing interventional treatment for sarcopenia;
